{"tid":1748604,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"有線新聞投訴前線人員屢遭警員不合理和粗暴對待","createTime":"2019-11-23T18:04:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-23T18:17:39.000Z","uid":53062,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e6443fd038d122676a04216bf1d80736541d30c4","tid":1748604,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T18:04:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1644118/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E4%BF%AE%E4%BE%8B%E9%A2%A8%E6%B3%A2-%E6%9C%89%E7%B7%9A%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%E6%8A%95%E8%A8%B4%E5%89%8D%E7%B7%9A%E4%BA%BA%E5%93%A1%E5%B1%A2%E9%81%AD%E8%AD%A6%E5%93%A1%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%88%E7%90%86%E5%92%8C%E7%B2%97%E6%9A%B4%E5%B0%8D%E5%BE%85\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1644118%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E-%25E4%25BF%25AE%25E4%25BE%258B%25E9%25A2%25A8%25E6%25B3%25A2-%25E6%259C%2589%25E7%25B7%259A%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%25E6%258A%2595%25E8%25A8%25B4%25E5%2589%258D%25E7%25B7%259A%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%2593%25A1%25E5%25B1%25A2%25E9%2581%25AD%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%2593%25A1%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%2590%2588%25E7%2590%2586%25E5%2592%258C%25E7%25B2%2597%25E6%259A%25B4%25E5%25B0%258D%25E5%25BE%2585&d=z%2Bfr9BvhH3rd6UlN4MOb%2FnhUmc0vP2awQoWdJLgJf%2FY%3D&h=5fed8e67\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1644118%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E-%25E4%25BF%25AE%25E4%25BE%258B%25E9%25A2%25A8%25E6%25B3%25A2-%25E6%259C%2589%25E7%25B7%259A%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%25E6%258A%2595%25E8%25A8%25B4%25E5%2589%258D%25E7%25B7%259A%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%2593%25A1%25E5%25B1%25A2%25E9%2581%25AD%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%2593%25A1%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%2590%2588%25E7%2590%2586%25E5%2592%258C%25E7%25B2%2597%25E6%259A%25B4%25E5%25B0%258D%25E5%25BE%2585&h=583d4351\" target=\"_blank\">https://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1644118/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E4%BF%AE%E4%BE%8B%E9%A2%A8%E6%B3%A2-%E6%9C%89%E7%B7%9A%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%E6%8A%95%E8%A8%B4%E5%89%8D%E7%B7%9A%E4%BA%BA%E5%93%A1%E5%B1%A2%E9%81%AD%E8%AD%A6%E5%93%A1%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%88%E7%90%86%E5%92%8C%E7%B2%97%E6%9A%B4%E5%B0%8D%E5%BE%85</a><br />\n【修例風波】有線新聞投訴前線人員屢遭警員不合理和粗暴對待<br />\n<br />\n有線新聞部負責人到警察投訴課遞交投訴信。有線截圖<br />\n有線新聞部負責人到警察投訴課遞交投訴信。有線截圖<br />\n警員在示威衝突中，多次與前線記者發生爭拗推撞，不時有傳媒記者受傷或被捕。有線電視新聞就過去五個月採訪衝突事件時，警方多次不合理及粗暴對待前線採訪人員，向警察投訴課投訴。<br />\n<br />\n有線電視新聞部負責人中午到警察投訴課遞交投訴信，當中涉及23名前線人員遇到警察的不合理和粗暴對待，包括無理阻礙採訪、推撞記者、向記者噴胡椒噴劑、投擲催淚彈，以及發射水炮、以閃光電筒及強光燈照射記者、強行扯下記者防護面罩等。<br />\n<br />\n有線新聞強調，絕不接受任何針對記者的暴力和蓄意阻礙採訪，促請警方公正徹底調查。"},{"pid":"ae69d698ac1e8a0b9cb6c31a1b505d20aca9e57a","tid":1748604,"uid":63117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T18:06:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7710cd89ae007b7c3533ca9daba92366cfc8e77","tid":1748604,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T18:09:09.000Z","msg":"大家可以down有線新聞app支持，免費，HDR高清<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://apps.apple.com/hk/app/%E6%9C%89%E7%B7%9A%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/id1433886832\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapps.apple.com%2Fhk%2Fapp%2F%25E6%259C%2589%25E7%25B7%259A%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2Fid1433886832&d=z%2Bfr9BvhH3rd6UlN4MOb%2FnhUmc0vP2awQoWdJLgJf%2FY%3D&h=5279f42f\" target=\"_blank\">https://apps.apple.com/hk/app/%E6%9C%89%E7%B7%9A%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/id1433886832</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=hk.hkott.app\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fstore%2Fapps%2Fdetails%3Fid%3Dhk.hkott.app&d=z%2Bfr9BvhH3rd6UlN4MOb%2FnhUmc0vP2awQoWdJLgJf%2FY%3D&h=baaeeb04\" target=\"_blank\">https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=hk.hkott.app</a>"},{"pid":"45f8ce27e7823b99cc36419cb94f27877f4edb51","tid":1748604,"uid":30836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-1